<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Chisʋs pulla hatuk mak o̱,
 Himak nitak oka,
 Ʋba Pi̱ki Chihowa ma!
 E chi hoho̱yoshke.

[V2]
 Ish pi̱ nukha̱klo pulla cha,
 Aboha ilʋppa
 Chi shilombish achukma ka
 Auet ish pimashke.

[V3]
 Hatak pilbʋsha fehna hosh,
 Chishno pulla kak o̱,
 Anumpa ilbʋsha yoka
 E chim asilhhʋshke.

[V4]
 Ʋba Pi̱ki binili ma!
 Ik yʋmohmi pulla,
 Et ish pim ahni pullashke,
 E chim ahni hoke.

[V5]
 Chi Shilombish pulla hoka
 Ish pi nukfokashke,
 Ahnit, aboha ilʋppa
 E chim asilhhʋshke.</lyrics>
<time_sig>C.M. (8.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<title>Chisʋs pulla hatuk mak o ƲIT127</title>
<author>Loring S. Williams</author>
<hymn_number>127</hymn_number>
</song>